    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to get this beauty into a new home! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so you\u2019re getting something truly special. The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream! You\u2019ve really got to see it to believe how pristine it is. I'm happy to answer any questions or show you around the car, so just give me a shout!",
      "price": 43500.0,
