    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe, a 6-speed manual gearbox, and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension is tuned with Bilstein PSS10 coilovers for optimized kinematic response, while the exterior retains its original deep luster. Mechanically flawless with a comprehensive service history, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance and analog driver engagement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
