    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed on a regular basis. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free of any swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show zero wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced driver-assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full documented service history from the local dealership and a smooth, powerful engine that feels as tight as the day it rolled off the assembly line. The alloy wheels are curb-rash free and wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
